{"tid":1424654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係拎走呢句！ 光復香港 時代革命","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:11:28.000Z","uid":299729,"like":10,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7bee7f72abd47566a42d647ff107053db3cbee","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"勇武 和理非 淺黃 中間 銀髮 香港有良知嘅人 甚至淺藍<br />\n我哋要攞最大嘅公因數 <br />\n對著要到嘅目標 <br />\n真係拎走呢句！ 光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n<br />\n大家夠多人 齊心 試下走去成功呢邊<br />\n跪求，口號叫返 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"bdeaae82e3878ab09093ebcfb1edd95602fc25c0","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"自推 10"},{"pid":"a1c25776f7a071f240b29faddb22c2bc626f577c","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7b68792ee3294be1a98fc32816ecbd797f8a2791","tid":1424654,"uid":36158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"你咪你又你叫囉<br />\n點解係都要拎走人"},{"pid":"a049de0dea6fbf6b99e771277274d41d68fb3de5","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"c8bf5ceaf3565dd36a1b2385f66e89d37b76d8ce","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"45ac834d1ca07c0cc7f791baebd6ee075014c05a","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a8ba6e753267f5ac4cc3101a6dcd1c91990478cd","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:18:17.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"4c2062cb8967e7187f2a99f470178f18c6db9db9","tid":1424654,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"680a93fd54d155b5de29fab6ed